string-array.name: help_aim_en
string-array.item: - Try to collect as much gifts as you can.
- Make as many \"hohos\" jumps as possible.
- Fly as long as you can through the worlds.
Beware of the morning light. It tries to catch
up to you. And morning light is the worst thing for santa!

string-array.name: task_help
string-array.item: To complete a task, you have to finish all three sub-parts you see listed, inside a single game. Once a task is finished it will be permanent. You will get rewarded by a score multiplicator for each finished task.

Um eine Aufgabe zu erfllen musst du alle drei aufgelisteten Unterpunkte in einem Spiel beenden. Wenn eine Aufgabe erfllt wurde, bleibt diese permanent erfllt. Du wirst nach jeder erfllten Aufgabe mit einem Punktemultiplikator belohnt.

"Per completare un compito, necessario terminare tutte e tre le sotto-parti che vedete elencate all'interno del singolo gioco. Una volta che un compito finito sarete ricompensati da un moltiplicatore di punti per ogni attivit finita."

string-array.item: "In endless mode no tasks available. Please try story mode to complete tasks."

"In endless mode no tasks available. Please try story mode to complete tasks."
"Nella modalit senza livelli nessun compito disponibile. Prova a giocare con i livelli per completare i compiti."
